{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/clone-an-element-using-jquery","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"jquery","demoType":null,"title":"Kopiraj element koristeći jQuery","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pored pomeranja elemenata, možete takođe da ih kopirate sa jedne lokacije na drugu.</p>\n<p>jQuery ima funkciju nazvanu <code>clone()</code> koja pravi kopiju elementa.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako bismo hteli da kopiramo <code>target2</code> iz našeg <code>left-well</code> do <code>right-well</code>, koristimo:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">$(\"#target2\").clone().appendTo(\"#right-well\");\n</code></pre>\n<p>Da li ste videli da ovo uključuje povezivanje dve jQuery funkcije? Ovo se zove <dfn>lančano spajanje funkcija</dfn> i to je jednostavan način za rad sa jQuery-jem.</p>\n<p>Kopiraj svoj element <code>target5</code> i zalepi ga u svoj <code>left-well</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed508826","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16780,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/clone-an-element-using-jquery"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(\"#target1\").css(\"color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").prop(\"disabled\", true);\r\n    $(\"#target4\").remove();\r\n    $(\"#target2\").appendTo(\"#right-well\");\r\n\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"conta